### Paymanager — Payment Flow
### Requires: Silvergate running on :3002, Paymanager on :3000, Ingest on :3001

@base = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health/ready

### -----------------------------------------------
### Create & Check Payment
### -----------------------------------------------

### 1. Create payment (triggers auth + capture via Silvergate)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "card_token": "tok_visa_4242"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("payment_id", response.body.id);
    client.log("Payment ID: " + response.body.id);
    client.log("Status: " + response.body.status);
    client.log("Provider TX: " + response.body.provider_tx_id);
%}

### 2. Get payment status (run after ~1s to see captured)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/payments/{{payment_id}}

> {%
    client.log("Status: " + response.body.status);
%}

### -----------------------------------------------
### More payments
### -----------------------------------------------

### 3. Another payment — higher amount
POST {{base}}/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 99900,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "card_token": "tok_mc_1234"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("payment_id_2", response.body.id);
    client.log("Status: " + response.body.status);
%}

### 4. Invalid request (expect 400)
POST {{base}}/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": -100,
  "currency": "XXXX",
  "card_token": ""
}

### 5. Non-existent payment (expect 404)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/payments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
